msgctxt "mn147:9.1"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃ passaṃ, rāhula, sutavā ariyasāvako cakkhusmiṃ nibbindati, rūpesu "
"nibbindati, cakkhuviññāṇe nibbindati, cakkhusamphasse nibbindati, yamidaṃ "
"cakkhusamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedanāgataṃ saññāgataṃ saṅkhāragataṃ "
"viññāṇagataṃ tasmimpi nibbindati."
msgstr ""
"“Seeing this, a learned noble disciple grows disillusioned with the eye, "
"sights, eye consciousness, and eye contact. And they grow disillusioned with "
"anything included in feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness that "
"arises conditioned by eye contact."

msgctxt "mn147:9.2"
msgid "Sotasmiṃ nibbindati, saddesu nibbindati … pe …"
msgstr "They grow disillusioned with the ear …"

msgctxt "mn147:9.3"
msgid "ghānasmiṃ nibbindati, gandhesu nibbindati …"
msgstr "nose …"

msgctxt "mn147:9.4"
msgid "jivhāya nibbindati, rasesu nibbindati …"
msgstr "tongue …"

msgctxt "mn147:9.5"
msgid "kāyasmiṃ nibbindati, phoṭṭhabbesu nibbindati …"
msgstr "body …"

msgctxt "mn147:9.6"
msgid ""
"manasmiṃ nibbindati, dhammesu nibbindati, manoviññāṇe nibbindati, "
"manosamphasse nibbindati, yamidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedanāgataṃ "
"saññāgataṃ saṅkhāragataṃ viññāṇagataṃ tasmimpi nibbindati."
msgstr ""
"mind, thoughts, mind consciousness, and mind contact. And they grow "
"disillusioned with anything included in feeling, perception, choices, and "
"consciousness that arises conditioned by mind contact."

msgctxt "mn147:9.7"
msgid ""
"Nibbindaṃ virajjati, virāgā vimuccati. Vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""
"Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re "
"freed. When they’re freed, they know they’re freed."

msgctxt "mn147:9.8"
msgid ""
"‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānātī”ti."
msgstr ""
"They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been "
"completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any "
"state of existence.’”"

