#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "mn147:9.9"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "mn147:9.10"
msgid "Attamano āyasmā rāhulo bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandīti."
msgstr "Satisfied, Venerable Rāhula was happy with what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "mn147:9.11"
msgid ""
"Imasmiñca pana veyyākaraṇasmiṃ bhaññamāne āyasmato rāhulassa anupādāya "
"āsavehi cittaṃ vimucci."
msgstr ""
"And while this discourse was being spoken, Rāhula’s mind was freed from "
"defilements by not grasping."

msgctxt "mn147:9.12"
msgid ""
"Tāsañca anekānaṃ devatāsahassānaṃ virajaṃ vītamalaṃ dhammacakkhuṃ udapādi:"
msgstr ""
"And the stainless, immaculate vision of the Dhamma arose in those thousands "
"of deities:"

msgctxt "mn147:9.13"
msgid "“yaṃ kiñci samudayadhammaṃ sabbaṃ taṃ nirodhadhamman”ti."
msgstr "“Everything that has a beginning has an end.”"

